# Dispute + AI Integration

**Rule:** For any dispute flow in any platform/app in this codebase, integrate with the existing AI system. Do not add dispute handling without AI.

## What to do

1. **When adding or changing dispute logic**
   - Use `analyzeDispute()` from `@/lib/market/ai` (same module used by Marketplace and SupaScrow).
   - Store AI result on the dispute record: `ai_decision` (refund | release | manual_review), `ai_reasoning`, `ai_confidence`.
   - Apply auto-resolve when confidence and amount thresholds are met (reuse or mirror `MARKET_AI_*` / `SUPASCROW_AI_*` style env and logic).

2. **Admin / solo-dev experience**
   - In admin dispute views, show suggested resolution (do not label as AI in UI) (decision + confidence + reasoning).
   - Provide a one-click “Apply suggestion” (or equivalent) so the human can accept the AI decision without re-reading every case.

3. **Reference implementations**
   - Marketplace: `src/app/api/market/dispute/route.ts` (open dispute → AI analyze → optional auto-resolve).
   - SupaScrow: `src/app/api/supascrow/route.ts` (action `dispute` → `analyzeDispute` → update dispute + optional auto-resolve); admin panel shows AI suggestion and “Apply suggestion”.

## Wording (all platforms)

Use the same neutral wording everywhere — Market, SupaScrow, and any future platform with disputes. **Never** show "AI", "AI Reply", "AI Confidence", "AI Support", etc. to users.

| Use (neutral) | Avoid |
|---------------|--------|
| Suggested resolution | AI decision / AI: |
| Apply suggestion | Apply AI / Accept AI |
| Suggested reply | AI Reply: |
| Confidence: X% | AI Confidence: |
| Support Assistant | AI Support Assistant |
| Get support routing / Checking... | Get AI Support Triage / Analyzing... |
| Our team will review and resolve it shortly. | Our AI will review... |
| Submitting... | AI Reviewing... |
| fair / secure dispute resolution | AI dispute resolution |
| Dispute resolution (hero/label) | Dispute AI / AI |

Reference: Market order page, Market admin disputes tab, SupaScrow public + admin, Market landing hero.

## Quick check

- New or modified dispute flows call `analyzeDispute()` and persist `ai_decision` / `ai_reasoning` / `ai_confidence`.
- Auto-resolve is gated by confidence and amount (with env-configurable limits).
- Admin UI shows suggested resolution and one-click apply — **never label as "AI"** in user- or buyer-facing copy; use the wording table above.
